Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Child
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya Ebata...\NWonder Child
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Child
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As you are top of the medical school class,\NWonder Child
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As you are top of the medical school class,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to give the congratulatory address \Nat next year's matriculation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I am pleased to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, he left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Look, it's Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant as always, Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, we should be \Nin the black this month! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So by strongly highlighting scarcity \Nthrough a focus on out-of-print goods,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it's increased demand, even in niche products?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Paradise Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant as expected, Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected a membership system \Nto bring this many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, Pops, it's not a membership system, \Nit's a subscription model service!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna play a fighting game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomita Baths       Coin Laundry 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I do appreciate you driving me \Nto my part-time jobs.\NTomita Baths       Coin Laundry 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A public bath really is best \Nafter business hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out, I get to \Nboldly soak in the women's bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't clean if you're in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's this month's pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to Kaga again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're a student. \NIt's important to have fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you become a doctor, \Nyou'll be busy every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring back souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll kindly accept your offer, \Nand request the usual Kaga treat, "kintsuba."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone at the senior center \Nwill be thrilled with that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're taking a while to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent, this is a true badge of honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You really didn't need to fight \Nuntil you were beat up this badly, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you don't fight, \Nyou won't be able to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that "winning"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never know unless you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... lift my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a matter of heart! \NYou fight in order to win, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that look for?! \NYou've gotta have an adventurous spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're riding in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we need to have the wind blowing at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's throwing away the greatest advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great to let your hair \Njust trail in the wind as we race along?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no hair, Masanori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so unromantic. \NYou've gotta have an adventurous spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit talking like this guy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying that means I win, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you've never once won against Danji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did my quip tick you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, you're totally mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so worked up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That tendency is how you get tripped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not tripped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My assumptions were naive, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have you watched that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,At least look at me for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That at some point, you'll feel that \Ncasual moments like this were the happiest ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about \NDanji announcing his retirement?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be back soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid who led him to retire, what is he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just some poor kid \Nwho got caught up in Danji's whims.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Really something, for the top med-school student \Nat Teito University to get this frantic about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:07:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll bring it to an end this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like quitting before ever beating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's high time for me to graduate \Nfrom playing games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Each person's life has \Na form that it's meant to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A form it's meant to take...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And which form would this be, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 'cause the rice cooker's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some bread for tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unsafe, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're from Danji's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the cute girl who was \Nreally cheering on Danji from the audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There were two of them, remember? \NThis is the one who was in girls' clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Makeup is incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Out shopping at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You like Salisbury steak with a fried egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Yu-yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A fried egg on top makes it feel special, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat while it's still warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do they seem so in-synch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you were in girls' clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a hobby of mine or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You could start that hobby, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It really didn't feel weird on you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you have more important things \Nto pay attention to at the time, Tohya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you really impressed me in that match!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I impressed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you kept attacking \Nover and over was just so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's the purpose of \N"fighting in order to win."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was something Danji told me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"You fight in order to win, right?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight in order to win, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, who'll fight me next?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're just too strong, Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, say!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had this deck, \Nhow would you make it even stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay with me looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't that basically \Nshowing your hand to an opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be glad if I could fight you someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but at my current level...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha. Okay, I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! Wow, this isn't bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's put together very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this rather remixed via substitutions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got advice from Danji and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If I combine this with this, \Nit'll be even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? You look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya, you've loved Vanguard \Nsince you were a kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I just assumed that for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, even Tohya was a kid at one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, why are you so fixated on Danji, Tohya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cutting to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, while Danji is pretty amazing, \Nto come this deep into the countryside...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to fight this deep in the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, Danji is just a bit special.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty wins in a row, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never met such a devil-may-care guy before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to fight him, and win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd travel anywhere in order to \Nexperience a moment like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight him, and win, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...get back to the life I was meant to lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What, ya can't fight seriously \Nunless in girls' clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start doing my best now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,With his indomitable spirit \Nand refreshing card handling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up.\NWith his indomitable spirit \Nand refreshing card handling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,With his indomitable spirit \Nand refreshing card handling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu's showing himself to be a fine young--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he making another challenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But didn't Danji retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to keep that promise to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about your flag \Nor the rights to the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to have a serious Cardfight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's come a very long way just for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not fighting him would kinda \Ngo against basic human morality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you chose a bad time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji is in poor condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In the remote region of Kaga dwelled a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...who continued to accept the challenges \Nof powerful enemies, to protect a flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter the time, or the challenger, \Nthe man faced them, never once running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And the flag still flies \Nbehind that man to this very day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:13:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's seen fighters from \Nthroughout this country of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is the only one I acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I came this far expecting to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And he would never turn his back on a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't right now, Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you unable to lift your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When he's selling that earnest an argument, \NI can't not buy into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But still!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji, don't get a newbie \Nwrapped up in your whims!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Descending once again \Nto this field on this night!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Solitary Fighter, Tohya Ebata!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And accepting his challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is our New Hope, Yu-yu Kondo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we just get this over with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn! I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Rino!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn! I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I call Painkiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fort attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Painkiller attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not nice enough \Nto hold back against a newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not nice enough to hand anyone a win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,OverDress!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That is how it'd go, knowing your deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiyu attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Arcs attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Phanuel attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Arcs intercepts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rooks attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fort attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu endured Tohya's full-force attack\N and is still at only 2 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows how this will turn out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. You just aren't \Nin the right frame of mind yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, this is a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Nirvana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Its skill activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I call Trickstar from the Drop Zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,OverDress!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nirvana attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! What am I doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...quit playing card games?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,After this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They say special children \Nshow differences even from a young age,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but a child like him could be a doctor someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the top score again! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better splurge on \Na nice birthday present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just study.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Play is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to tell your mother and father
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that these cards will make you smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let things end here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna beat Danji, \Nand then quit playing card games!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A greenhorn like you shouldn't be \Nstanding there, blocking my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Bastion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I move Fort to the back row!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I call! I call! I call! I call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Calls to fill it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he trying to finish the match on this turn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll strike you with my greatest firepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Boosted by Fort, Rooks attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved the throb of my heartbeat \Nthat I could only hear while fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,His scores haven't dropped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But couldn't they be even higher \Nif he wasn't playing cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes home late every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're still asking me \Nto let him do as he likes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd never been one \Nto play with toys before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So you got too engrossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely understand that \Nplaying games is more fun than studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I indulged myself with darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I started to frequent Cardfighting spaces, \Nkeeping away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiyu intercepts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you quitting Vanguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you? I'm going back to \Nthe life I was meant to lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna quit this game already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NDo you really--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:19:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You should do what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You play cards, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to hang around at \Nthat Cardfighting spot every day, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you been by lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredibly, Yu-yu has withstood \Nthat bombardment, taking only 1 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight is far from over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand and draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,OverDress!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Vairina Valiente!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When this unit's attack hits,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it can stand and attack one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu has progressed to his strongest card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Boosted by Velocihazard, \NNirvana attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Over Trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Valiente gets +100 million power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That ambition compares favorably \Nto a warrior of long military service!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I too will take that challenge, \Nwith all my body and soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tusk won't get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This Sword of the Ruler \Nwill be the only one to do any slaying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about you, Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you're thinking of quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, all I can do is beat you up! \NWith everything I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I, too, will risk everything I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get that tusk of yours to fracture!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pierce through!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you had yet another tusk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.53,0:22:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I won the Vanguard tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get ready. \NYou'll be late for cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This really...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...isn't a game to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.41,0:25:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Out My Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.11,0:25:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.29,0:26:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll introduce Vairina Valiente!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.77,0:26:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Valiente is a unit that you can \Nfurther overDress onto Vairina!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.73,0:26:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a skill that gives it \N+5000 power for each original Dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.82,0:26:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and another that lets it attack again \Nafter a successful attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.86,0:26:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Valiente gets stronger with each layer it wears,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.95,0:26:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning... that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.45,0:26:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go out and buy some new clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.27,0:26:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.33,0:26:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.34,0:26:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Runny Porridge
